WEBVTT

00:00:29.150 --> 00:00:31.170
Nisu otkrili konkretan razlog

00:00:31.170 --> 00:00:35.832
osim da sam malo disleksičan jer sam
ljevoruk.

00:00:35.832 --> 00:00:39.807
Ali nisu testirali moju radoznalost.

00:00:39.807 --> 00:00:42.388
Za mene, radoznalost

00:00:42.388 --> 00:00:44.361
se odnosi na našu povezanost

00:00:44.361 --> 00:00:46.876
sa svijetom i svemirom.

00:00:46.876 --> 00:00:49.496
Na želju da vidimo šta
je iza koraljne kolonije

00:00:49.496 --> 00:00:51.195
ili iza onog drveta

00:00:51.195 --> 00:00:53.254
i da naučimo više ne samo o
našem okruženju

00:00:53.254 --> 00:00:55.324
nego i on nama samima.

00:00:55.324 --> 00:00:57.854
San mojih snova

00:00:57.854 --> 00:01:01.128
je da istražujem Marsove okeane